In your DAO or service class, where you perform the Hibernate queries:

```java
public class AnimalService {

    // Get all Cats from the database
    public List<Cat> getAllCats() {
        // Hibernate query to fetch all Cats
    }

    // Get all Dogs from the database
    public List<Dog> getAllDogs() {
        // Hibernate query to fetch all Dogs
    }

    // Combine Cats and Dogs into a single list of Animals
    public List<Animal> getAllAnimals() {
        List<Animal> animals = new ArrayList<>();
        animals.addAll(getAllCats());
        animals.addAll(getAllDogs());

        return animals;
    }
}
```

